話之你皮膚白到塗改液咁</blockquote><br />\n唔係一白遮三醜咖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一白遮三醜，遮左都咁撚醜，死左佢好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好彩自問個樣合格有餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1190d8880cea72fe114add6cb9ec5a05b931d204","tid":144990,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11885e77167d2f3554d9fd691a15c5b02af703da","tid":144990,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排染左金色 一開頭個個都話mk<br />\n但之後就話發覺金色襯我 更顯白<br />\n<br />\n染到淺色要keep住化妝<br />\n如果唔係就會顯得好殘</blockquote><br />\n無諗住染淺色，怕好殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n染外國人果隻紅洗唔洗漂咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad74d481cff7c3360c354391c879ba2a73c721a","tid":144990,"uid":53885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:04:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黑or啡<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n可能我睇得太多五顏六色頭好古怪 都係<span style=\"color: red;\">中</span>意黑啡原汁原味<br />\n<br />\n利申絲</blockquote><br />\n鍾</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「鍾意」是廣東話, 意思是喜歡, 愛. 書面語無此詞語. 但查辭典(台灣教育部國語辭典 http://140.111.1.22/mandr/clc/dict): <br />\n<br />\n「鍾愛」 = 特別疼愛。[北史˙卷十二˙隋煬帝本紀：上美姿儀，少敏慧，高祖及后於諸子中，特所鍾愛。三國演義˙第十六回：惟嚴氏生一女，布最鍾愛。] <br />\n<br />\n「鍾情」 = 專情愛慕。如：一見鍾情。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於「中意」, 也是一個正確的書面語, 意思係合意、滿意。[漢書˙卷四十五˙江充傳：奉法不阿，所言中意。初刻拍案驚奇˙卷三：老身虛心冷氣，看他眉頭眼後，常是不中意，受他凌辱的。] <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意思類似「o岩聽」. <br />\n<br />\n所以要真的要寫的話, 「鍾意」比較正確. 而且「中意」的「中」讀「種」音(同「中獎」「中傷」, 「中規中距」等情況), 不是讀「鍾」音. <br />\n2006-05-22 19:11:02 補充 <br />\n以上只適用於口語廣東話, 考試不可以真的寫「鍾意」. 而且如果是考辨認錯別字, 「鍾意」是別字,「中意」才是正確. <br />\n<br />\n來源:<a href=\"http://hk.knowledge.yahoo.com/question/question?qid=7006052201558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.knowledge.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Fquestion%3Fqid%3D7006052201558&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ad3c3b8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.knowledge.yahoo.com/question/question?qid=7006052201558</a>"},{"pid":"97bdfb6b4259f47327588864d70dc7096ee716e3","tid":144990,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你的樣子如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果本身係皮膚白又襯咖呢？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/095226_09906d72b5038bab55ae6ab18e3b0dae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F095226_09906d72b5038bab55ae6ab18e3b0dae.jpg&h=c7cdd24a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e358b1df3490459e4be00d6c67f773e948f0c08","tid":144990,"uid":21096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前排染左金色 一開頭個個都話mk<br />\n但之後就話發覺金色襯我 更顯白<br />\n<br />\n染到淺色要keep住化妝<br />\n如果唔係就會顯得好殘</blockquote><br />\n無諗住染淺色，怕好殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n染外國人果隻紅洗唔洗漂咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係睇你本身髮色同髮質<br />\n如果又黑又粗 齋染就好難上色"},{"pid":"bd7722948e5139b283418d5f61d95a58998d58b3","tid":144990,"uid":72828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"h